Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.95,-1:59:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.95,-1:59:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.95,-1:59:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要補償的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「蒼穹之戰神」第22話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護 - 力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
